title: 11/27/2020 – Hour 2 – The Final Nail in the Coffin for Tom Brady
itunes:title: 11/27/2020 – Hour 2 – The Final Nail in the Coffin for Tom Brady
description:
Rob Parker argues that Tom Brady is the weak link for the Tampa Bay Buccaneers and Jason McIntyre defends the six-time Super Bowl champion. The guys finally settle the G.O.A.T. discussion and explain why college football has been a tough watch this year!
